---
// Engagement Models section for Professional Services industry page
---

<section id="engagement" class="cre-engagement-section">
  <div class="cre-engagement-container">
    <span class="section-label">ENGAGEMENT MODELS</span>
    <h2 class="cre-engagement-headline">
      How we structure professional services partnerships
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-engagement-grid">
      <!-- Build + Maintain -->
      <div class="cre-engagement-card">
        <h3 class="cre-engagement-card-title">Build + Maintain</h3>
        <p class="cre-engagement-card-description">
          We architect and build your professional services systems, then transfer ownership to your team. You maintain and evolve the platform with our support as needed.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-engagement-structure">
          <p class="cre-structure-label">Structure:</p>
          <ul class="cre-structure-list">
            <li>Custom system development</li>
            <li>Knowledge transfer and training</li>
            <li>Ongoing support on retainer</li>
            <li>Full system ownership</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Build + Operate -->
      <div class="cre-engagement-card">
        <h3 class="cre-engagement-card-title">Build + Operate</h3>
        <p class="cre-engagement-card-description">
          We build and operate your systems, handling infrastructure, updates, and maintenance. You focus on delivery while we ensure your technology runs smoothly.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-engagement-structure">
          <p class="cre-structure-label">Structure:</p>
          <ul class="cre-structure-list">
            <li>Custom system development</li>
            <li>Full operational management</li>
            <li>Continuous updates and improvements</li>
            <li>24/7 system monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Managed Systems -->
      <div class="cre-engagement-card">
        <h3 class="cre-engagement-card-title">Managed Systems</h3>
        <p class="cre-engagement-card-description">
          We take full responsibility for your professional services technology stack—from architecture through operations. You get enterprise-grade systems without building an internal tech team.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-engagement-structure">
          <p class="cre-structure-label">Structure:</p>
          <ul class="cre-structure-list">
            <li>End-to-end system management</li>
            <li>Strategic technology roadmap</li>
            <li>Dedicated operations team</li>
            <li>Performance optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-engagement-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-engagement-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-engagement-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-engagement-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-engagement-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    padding: 32px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-engagement-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .cre-engagement-card:hover .cre-engagement-card-title {
    color: #000000;
  }

  .cre-engagement-card:hover .cre-engagement-card-description {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cre-engagement-card:hover .cre-structure-label {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cre-engagement-card:hover .cre-structure-list li {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  .cre-engagement-card-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-engagement-card-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-engagement-structure {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: border-color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-engagement-card:hover .cre-engagement-structure {
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .cre-structure-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-structure-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-structure-list li {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-structure-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #0EA5E9;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-engagement-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-engagement-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-engagement-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

